{"title":"EPOC exacerbado-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neumología/EPOC exacerbado-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"EPOC\\Nexacerbado","guid":"nMPxDP6-EiTP7W_yMqKiCQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Perlas:","guid":"vfy-n1wK7bG8mVQHxG67FQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cómo se define una\\Nexacerbación de EPOC?","guid":"YalBcLHXwyPwQe03YiR2tA","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Empeoramiento agudo de los síntomas respiratorios\\Nque requiere tratamiento adicional (1).","guid":"g4YQjqxp6DWYpSCKS8IZsA","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuáles son las causas más\\Nfrecuentes de exacerbación de EPOC?","guid":"ooLx-dm69zu6p9DFX16uKg","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Infecciones respiratorias virales (30-50%)\\Ny bacterianas (40-50%) (2,3).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Qué factores se asocian a un mayor\\Nriesgo de exacerbaciones frecuentes?","guid":"XnHEI9H5it7d_QmWdRzslw","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"VEF1 reducido, exacerbaciones previas, bronquiectasias,\\Nenfisema e inflamación de vía aérea (4,5).","guid":"Q_X5MV4MEPVd3fO3wHGU8A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Descompensado","guid":"zV_W39dz0ZMm4_gK3A4p4A","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Criterios de Anthonisen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Aumento disnea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Aumento tos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"Incremento volumen o\\Ncambio de color del esputo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Signología obstructiva","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"8","text":"Clasificar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"FR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"Conciencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"Musculatura accesoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"Hipoxemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"Hipercabnia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"8","text":"Pruebas complementaria\\N¿Causa descompensante?","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Siempre","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Hemograma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Perfil bioquímico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Radiografía de tórax","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Electrocardiograma","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"20","text":"Según sospecha","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Dímero D","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Angio TAC tórax","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Ecocardiograma","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"8","text":"Tratamiento\\NMinimizar impacto - Prevenir recurrir","guid":"","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Soporte\\Nrespiratorio","guid":"-U9FfSH9Uz6DCRuks9Xvjw","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"O2 0,5-1 l/min\\NFiO2 para saturar 88-92%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Control periódico de gases arteriales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"Considerar ventilación mecánica no invasiva\\NIndicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"Acidosis respiratoria\\N(PaCO2≥45 mmHg - pH≤7.35)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"Disnea severa con signos clínicos\\Nsugerentes de fatiga muscular y/o\\Naumento de trabajo respiratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Uso musculatura accesoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Movimiento paradójico del abdomen","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"Retracción intercostal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"34","text":"Hipoxemia persistente pese a oxigenoterapia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"31","text":"Indicación de UCI","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Disnea severa que responde de forma inadecuada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Compromiso de\\Nconciencia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Confusión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Letargia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"Coma","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"41","text":"Hipoxemia que empeora o persiste\\N(PaO2<40)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"41","text":"Acidosis respiratoria que empeora o persiste\\N(pH < 7.25)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"41","text":"Inestabilidad hemodinámica que necesita vasopresores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"41","text":"Indicación de ventilación mecánica invasiva","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"30","text":"Broncodilatación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Nebulización con aire +\\NSABA con o sin SAMA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Salbutamol\\N1ml en 3ml de SF","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"Ipratropio\\N1ml en 3ml de SF","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"30","text":"Corticoides\\N5 a 7 días","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Mejoran VEF1, oxigenación, disminuye\\Ntiempo recuperación y hospitalización","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Prednisona 30-40 mg/día.","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Preferir","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"Hidrocortisona 100 mg c/8h.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"30","text":"Antibioticoterapia\\N5 a 7 días","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Disminuye tiempo de recuperación, falla\\Nde tratamiento y duración hospitalización.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"Indicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Exacerbación severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"Leve a moderada con esputo\\Npurulento y/o PCR elevada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"60","text":"MINSAL","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Amoxicillina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"Macrolidos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"60","text":"Exacerbación moderada\\NH. influenzae - S. pneumoniae - M. catarrhalis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"Amoxicilina/Ác. Clavulánico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"Ceftriaxona","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"Levofloxacino","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"60","text":"Exacerbación severa o \\NRiesgo PSAU","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Factores de\\Nriesgo PSAU","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"Deterioro severo de función pulmonar (VEF1<50%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"Bronquiectasias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"Cardiopatía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"Exacerbación previa por PSAU","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"Colonización bronquial por PSAU","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"73","text":"ATB en tres meses previos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"73","text":"Hospitalización reciente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"73","text":"Uso corticoides orales (prednisona >10 mg/día)\\Nen las últimas 2 semanas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"72","text":"Ciprofloxacino","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"72","text":"Levofloxacino en altas dosis","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"30","text":"Identificar y tratar\\Ncondiciones asociadas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"SCA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"IC descompensada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"Arritmia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"TEP","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"30","text":"Otros","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Observación al menos dos horas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"Monitorizar balance hídrico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"Considerar profilaxis tromboembólica con\\Nheparina no fraccionada o de bajo peso molecular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"Iniciar terapia de mantención con LABA o\\NLAMA cuando este estable, previo al alta.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"30","text":"Hospitalización\\NMINSAL","guid":"","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"Presencia de comorbilidades descompensadas o de alto riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"Respuesta inadecuada al tratamiento ambulatorio de los síntomas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"94","text":"Incremento marcado de la disnea a pesar de la terapia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"94","text":"Hipoxemia progresiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"94","text":"Hipercapnia progresiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"94","text":"Deterioro del estado mental de ingreso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"94","text":"Incapacidad del paciente para cuidar de sí mismo\\N(red de apoyo social deficiente)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"94","text":"Inadecuado cuidado en el hogar","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"0","text":"Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"- Evento agudo caracterizado por empeoramiento de síntomas respiratorios\\Nmás allá de las variaciones diarias, que requiere cambio en el tratamiento (1).","guid":"yVb_aKNK618Nf4kAvDGh-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"- Desencadenada por infecciones, contaminación o causa desconocida. Aumenta\\Ninflamación de vía aérea con mayor producción de moco y broncoconstricción (6,7).","guid":"xPzGpRziqOp0DnVC9egN6A","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"- Estrés oxidativo, desequilibrio proteasas-antiproteasas e\\Ninflamación sistémica contribuyen al daño pulmonar (8).","guid":"IzYRZ_7c1gkPrRbszvcTVw","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"- Potenciales objetivos terapéuticos: Inhibir inflamación,\\Nreducir hipersecreción mucosa y prevenir infecciones (9).","guid":"FX-wx6X29QG_8De69KhCCg","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"- Frecuentes en EPOC, con media de 1-2 eventos/año. Causan significativa morbilidad,\\Ndeterioro de calidad de vida, declinación de función pulmonar y aumento de mortalidad (10-12).","guid":"vlLGwUPPZ06453tzTl_xqA","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"- En Chile, son causa frecuente de consulta en\\Nurgencias y hospitalizaciones (13).","guid":"p5GfEWt-TSK75Tc3v3x6HA","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"- Severidad de limitación del flujo aéreo (VEF1 <50% pred), exacerbaciones previas (≥2 en último año), comorbilidades\\N(enfermedad CV, RGE, ansiedad-depresión), inflamación sistémica elevada (PCR, fibrinógeno) (4,5,14,15).","guid":"pb8HlnAhS4crIzKyKvezKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"0","text":"Causas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"- Infecciones virales (rinovirus, influenza, parainfluenza, VRS) (30-50%), bacterianas (H. influenzae,\\NS. pneumoniae, M. catarrhalis) (40-50%), contaminación (10%), desconocida (10-30%) (1-3).","guid":"LxBiFwXLnr80Q1KrnVTy4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"- Aumento de disnea, tos, volumen-purulencia\\Nesputo, sibilancias, alteración signos vitales,\\Ninsuficiencia respiratoria (1).","guid":"TK7-7FMoCS2zaYHowTvaPg","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"- Criterios de Anthonisen: Presencia y\\Nseveridad de cambios en disnea, volumen\\Ny purulencia esputo (16).","guid":"JpLCFQZlw5FX4M2ZeYdxyQ","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"116","text":"- Factores de mal pronóstico: Edad >65, ≥3\\Nexacerbaciones/año, VEF1 <50%,\\Ncomorbilidades, bajo soporte social (17).","guid":"0eLR95hqmAmKbPPLG6PePQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"- Rx tórax: Descartar neumonía, neumotórax, ICC. Gases arteriales: Evaluar\\Nseveridad (PaO2 <60, PaCO2 >45 mmHg: mayor riesgo VM) (18,19).","guid":"2Rg1y-o6_zaHdMnUz7Jdzg","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"- Espirometría: No recomendada en exacerbación aguda. Cultivo expectoración:\\NExacerbaciones severas, falla tratamiento o necesidad VM (1,20).","guid":"lkvT7oOUaIByJqK9f11hyg","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"- Biomarcadores: PCR >10 mg/dL: infección bacteriana.\\NProcalcitonina: Controversial para guiar antibióticos (21).","guid":"1t1zQ58i-bMH2TiGAhtwpA","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"- Clínico. Criterios de Anthonisen: Tipo 1 (↑Disnea +\\Nvolumen + purulencia esputo), Tipo 2 (2 de 3), Tipo 3\\N(1 + síntomas infección) (16).","guid":"imatGu0WRwepvcjmED-pvA","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"- Severidad: Leve\\N(ambulatorio), Moderada\\N(hospitalización), Severa (VM)\\N(1).","guid":"jBR00ZTfLggodswaXXEamA","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"- Insuficiencia cardíaca, neumonía, neumotórax,\\Nembolia pulmonar, arritmias.","guid":"vb6lGeW7t_Bb3m_RxWaHgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"- Minimizar impacto y\\Nprevenir eventos futuros (1).","guid":"UbqkmqKq-tYw2HuX1jOtZw","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"- No farmacológico: Suspender\\Ntabaco, optimizar O2 (SpO2 88-92%),\\NVNI en falla hipercápnica.","guid":"XUiT3F9ZMuUYxWvwNPSi8w","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"0","text":"- Farmacológico (1):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"- Broncodilatadores: ↑Dosis/frecuencia SABA (Salbutamol 100-200mcg 4-6inh c/4-6h),\\NSAMA (Ipratropio 40-80mcg 4-6inh c/4-6h). Nebulizaciones en severas.","guid":"qErnJnvNHYfs9j9d3pH1vA","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"- Corticoides: Prednisona 40mg/d x 5d VO.\\NAlternativa: Metilprednisolona 0,5-1mg/kg/d IV.","guid":"TlJA1uDHCgA75spVVoyBFg","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"- Antibióticos (Criterios Anthonisen): Amoxicilina/Ac.Clavulánico 875/125mg c/12h\\No Cefuroxima 500mg c/12h x5-7d. Levofloxacino o Moxifloxacino en 2ª línea.","guid":"p-mgpXKdY7ar0rOBCjjIbw","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"132","text":"- Monitorizar efectos adversos: Hiperglicemia, retención\\Nhidrosalina, síntomas GI, prolongación QT.","guid":"kCqeKpfijUoIWv0IoZmiMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"- Control en 48-72h.\\NHospitalizar si no mejora (1).","guid":"RmKUg7dq9maA0_cy76tJeQ","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"137","text":"- Post-exacerbación: Control especialista 4-6\\Nsem. Revisar técnica inhalatoria, adherencia,\\Nrehabilitación pulmonar (22).","guid":"Wrc76GCbXrSnFps_a0EsFg","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"137","text":"- Mortalidad hospitalaria 2-15%, 40% al\\Naño en severas. Índice DECAF predice\\Nmortalidad a 30d (23,24).","guid":"SZf-SQ9VydU8-qQ3MmCWyA","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"0","text":"Prevención:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"- Cese tabaco, vacuna anti-influenza y\\Nantineumocócica, optimizar terapia\\N(LAMA/LABA, rehabilitación) (1).","guid":"2U_SBfoNXozHS8S2iKE99A","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"- Exacerbaciones frecuentes (≥2/año): Considerar\\Nmacrólido profiláctico (Azitromicina 250mg 3v/sem o\\NEritromicina 250-500mg 2v/d) (25).","guid":"w2K-qFvYDPiNuhcaETIcPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"0","text":"Tamizaje:","guid":"eIlNI2vWN4Q2jjn2ZKnETQ","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"- No recomendado. Alto índice de sospecha en\\NEPOC, especialmente en temporada infecciosa.","guid":"5wU_uDymN0Z-B02KFl7oNQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"0","text":"Aspectos Geriátricos:","guid":"GR2hDBn11UmKjrVVyqOlNQ","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"- Mayor riesgo de exacerbaciones severas y mortalidad.\\NPresentación atípica (Confusión, letargia, caídas). Considerar\\Ncomorbilidades, polifarmacia y ajuste de dosis (26,27).","guid":"p4AyYAAp5Qa2COyV52O4_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"M1mZFS_iVDOWtZYI6C6V6A","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"1. GOLD 2022. https://goldcopd.\\Norg/2022-gold-reports/","guid":"zbE_g_zoE_Yb_ld4mhCCsg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"2. Hewitt R, et al. Ther Adv Respir\\NDis. 2016;10(2):158-174.","guid":"Ba9Hy1JV__qgdphLTK4djw","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"3. Sethi S, Murphy TF. N Engl J Med.\\N2008;359(22):2355-2365.","guid":"cHxIfWYEF75Xqebmy9p3iw","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"148","text":"4. Hurst JR, et al. N Engl J Med.\\N2010;363(12):1128-1138.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"5. Han MK, et al. Am J Respir Crit Care\\NMed. 2010;182(5):598-604.","guid":"Uyw-yNSTObGXJ9iED6OJzA"